/**
 * @mainpage gocxx::errors
 * 
 * @section intro Introduction
 * 
 * The `gocxx::errors` library provides a Go-like error handling interface in C++.
 * It supports:
 * 
 * - Wrapping errors
 * - Unwrapping nested errors
 * - Type casting with `As`
 * - Comparing with `Is`
 * - Joining multiple errors
 * 
 * @section usage Usage
 * 
 * ```cpp
 * using namespace gocxx::errors;
 * auto err = New("simple error");
 * auto wrapped = Wrap("context", err);
 * ```
 * 
 * @see gocxx::errors::Error
 */
